{"tid":395414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林作：涼薄還涼薄，但言論就是言論自由。政府不是以言入罪是甚麼?","createTime":"2017-09-10T18:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T03:45:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6c1af03e2e05db9e99a9217841abcb246962aa4","tid":395414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:06:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170910/20148559?_ga=2.228877979.606128678.1504794239-7797648.1439036704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170910%2F20148559%3F_ga%3D2.228877979.606128678.1504794239-7797648.1439036704&d=3xCMysoeWQKAvrXOxL%2FWif755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=166eca9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170910%2F20148559%3F_ga%3D2.228877979.606128678.1504794239-7797648.1439036704&h=562d045c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170910/20148559?_ga=2.228877979.606128678.1504794239-7797648.1439036704</a><br />\n<br />\n周四有人在教育大學民主牆張貼「恭喜」教育局副局長蔡若蓮喪子的大字報，同時近日多間大學校園內發生張貼「港獨」標語的風波。教育局局長楊潤雄指言論自由並非全無底線，特首林鄭月娥更指是借學術自由和院校自主為藉口鼓吹歪論，期望社會各界人士應合力糾正這種「濫用言論自由」的行為。<br />\n<br />\n林作在社交網站上發表貼文，表示「涼薄還涼薄」，但言論就是言論自由，並無濫用與否之說，直指「這不是以言入罪是甚麼」。對於有人指言論自由應以不傷害他人為前提，他表示個人感受難以衡量言語的傷害性，而言論自由更是香港最寶貴的東西。"},{"pid":"700934e2ed3f1a51b72e5107d4e983cf2f6b94e6","tid":395414,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:07:24.000Z","msg":"佢唔係奶共架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdc76af4d4b37e8d0ad1d32c8aceab723c150bb","tid":395414,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔係奶共架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買兩邊"},{"pid":"18df805160bf1f568f4c0d3f5acba1f0a2f10ad9","tid":395414,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:13:57.000Z","msg":"抽政治油水，林作收撚皮啦"},{"pid":"fef864ed08fab295d5b90cb3c969cf2b5ba4929f","tid":395414,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係奶共架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買兩邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好大機會有英國護照"},{"pid":"309c6e30c1d971bf07e60e7af9728b08641488a9","tid":395414,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"陶傑win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921618fabae0e1c1c90f30a49ce4282becda3a9c","tid":395414,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係奶共架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買兩邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做補習，扮吓熱血吸客"},{"pid":"0d8e68011e4b562b59bd7ac4d5e2d549df36543e","tid":395414,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢唔係奶共架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買兩邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做補習，扮吓熱血吸客</blockquote><br />\n做間以年輕人為主要客人既補習班，點都要企係佢地果邊既"},{"pid":"b05fc827c0344fa0092521f1bf6993c31461b59f","tid":395414,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔係奶共架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都有角色分配<br />\n<br />\n佢要扮同年輕人岩key<br />\n都未到時候要撳制"},{"pid":"78f3b8c375e5df96c59b3caff6103a922b3557a5","tid":395414,"uid":16516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"做得律師呢d概念好基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed13c34ff1fa01294f074e686c394cdc6de63ba","tid":395414,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-